بدونها النظام ناقص

prompt


Build Doctor Availability Management UI.

Backend:
- CRUD for doctor availability:
  - day_of_week
  - start_time
  - end_time

Endpoints:
- GET /doctors/{id}/availability
- POST /doctors/{id}/availability
- DELETE /availability/{id}

Frontend:
- Page:
  /doctors/[id]/availability
- UI:
  - weekly schedule
  - add/edit time slots

UX:
- simple grid:
  Sunday → Saturday
- allow multiple slots per day

Rules:
- no overlap
- validate times

Return:
- files




💰 4. Billing / Invoices
الفكرة

هاي اللي بتخليك تبيع 💸

prompt


Implement basic billing system.

Backend:
- Create Invoice:
  - id
  - patient_id
  - appointment_id
  - amount
  - status (pending, paid)
  - created_at

Endpoints:
- POST /invoices
- GET /patients/{id}/invoices
- PATCH /invoices/{id}/pay

Frontend:
- In patient page:
  - invoices section
- Show:
  - amount
  - status
- Add "Mark as Paid"

Rules:
- invoice created on appointment

Return:
- files


